  <description>
    <p>
      Cardthropic is a Libadwaita and Rust solitaire app for GNOME, beginning
      with Klondike and an adaptive board designed for many window sizes.
    </p>
    <p>
      It includes seeded deals, undo/redo, smart move controls, autoplay wand,
      winnability checks, board themes, and persistent seed history.
    </p>
  </description>
